{"tid":2126537,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"領展進軍英國　3.8億英鎊收購The Cabot","createTime":"2020-07-27T01:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-27T07:01:07.000Z","uid":79563,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"92ee8c2ba0e4d3018716a5b87baa26b46d7c99a0","tid":2126537,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:48:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540018-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540018-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=EOe11knUQePtQJIakN8qx8%2BSO5qySt9BI5W58Aqq%2Fug%3D&h=fb282f12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1540018-20200727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=86dde130\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1540018-20200727.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n領展收購英國辦公大樓The Cabot，作價3.8億英鎊，相當於約37.7億港元，是領展首次收購英國資產。<br />\n<br />\n行政總裁王國龍表示，The Cabot能帶來穩健收入及即時收益增長，長遠亦具增長潛力。物業屬核心商業區甲級辦公大樓，亦是金絲雀碼頭少數永久業權物業。他又說，除香港及內地，集團正放眼具高透明度及流動性、良好法律體系及強健經濟基礎的市場，包括英國、新加坡、澳洲和日本，尋求收購機會。<br />\n<br />\nThe Cabot過去6年進行大規模翻新和擴建，今年3月完成。物業樓高17層，樓面面積超過48萬平方呎，現存租約加權平均約滿期近11年，每年租金淨收入1883萬英鎊，以收購價及收入計，投資收益率5%。目前物業有7名公司租戶，最大部分屬一家國際投資銀行，佔現時淨收入近一半，其次是一個非部長級政府部門，佔淨收入約25%。<br />\n<br />\n按截至3月底的財務狀況，交易完成後領展的備考經調整債務對資產總值比率將由17.8%上升至19.2%。"},{"pid":"8895d8082697d0afaaa2740600a061fa36221b68","tid":2126537,"uid":126325,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:48:53.000Z","msg":"823<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e09059736b00a82ca8d6b484077c663748743259","tid":2126537,"uid":6297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-27T01:49:38.000Z","msg":"跟李先生做無錯㗎喇"},{"pid":"331a7dfe0a0da49f6750eead37cc6459ee3d8a9c","tid"